{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "迦道夫（Fes限定Ver.） 第4话 父亲的背影",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈，我要去工作了。\\n等我回来，我们好好谈谈吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "要在家里好好等我回来……\\n我走了啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "好了，\\n早上的训练就到这里吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫兵",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队士兵",
            "context": "迦道夫大人看起来心不在焉呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "嗯，是有什么心事吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（本以为自己见识了各种世界，\\n但其实依旧才疏学浅。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（甚至连我最亲近的人的心情，\\n我竟然都猜不透……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "迦道夫大人，有一封寄给您的信。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "信？不是寄到家里，\\n而是寄到训练场来了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "送信人说因为家里没人，\\n所以才来了这边。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（席菈应该在家的，\\n她没有回应敲门吗？）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "也罢……给我看看吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "！\\n寄信人是亚罗拉斯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "我亲爱的朋友迦道夫。\\n看到你久违的来信，我很开心。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "你似乎为女儿的事情所烦恼，\\n我也能从你的字里行间\\n看出你非常爱她。\\n但我觉得你正是因此\\n才违背了自己的心。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "以前的你，定不会\\n对“贫民窟”的事情视而不见。\\n因为仍是国王时的你，\\n会对流离失所的人们伸出援手。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "席菈是看着你的背影长大的。\\n即使她的心已不在，\\n你的背影想必也\\n早已刻进她的脑海。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "那位会向弱者伸出援手的\\n父亲的背影……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（父亲的背影……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "他们正是对这个国家抱有希望，\\n才会拼死逃难到这里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "那么无论是作为一国之君，\\n还是作为一个心怀仁慈的人，\\n我都不能不出手相助。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "爸爸……我可不可以也去\\n帮忙为接收难民做准备？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "因为我既是勒福克斯的王族，\\n也更是您的女儿。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（即使心已不在，\\n我曾向她展示的为人之道\\n却还留在她的记忆之中。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（那么，在她看来，现在的我……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队士兵",
            "context": "报告！\\n“贫民窟”出现了魔兽！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队士兵",
            "context": "似乎是没有得到修理的缺口扩大，\\n导致魔兽从那里进来了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队士兵",
            "context": "教会骑士团似乎还要一段时间才能出动！\\n所以要求近卫队先行赶赴现场，\\n以避免更大的伤亡！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "教会骑士团那帮混蛋，\\n竟然在关键时刻磨磨蹭蹭……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "没时间抱怨了。\\n我们赶快前去“贫民窟”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "近卫队全体成员！迅速消灭魔兽！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "进来了相当多的魔兽啊。\\n嗯！？那是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120062_01",
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贫民窟的少女",
            "context": "哇啊啊啊，我怕……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "哈啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120062_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贫民窟的少女",
            "context": "啊！是士兵叔叔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "你们两个没事吧？\\n席菈，你怎么在这里？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120062_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贫民窟的少女",
            "context": "大姐姐是来帮忙的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "帮忙？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120062_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贫民窟的少女",
            "context": "因为墙壁的洞变大了，\\n所以我们一直在想办法修补。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120062_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贫民窟的少女",
            "context": "大姐姐每天都会来这里\\n帮我们一起修补……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "你为了帮助住在这里的人，\\n每天都会来这里吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（这是失去了心以后\\n只会听从命令的席菈\\n第一次主动采取行动。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（她也许不知道为自己难过。\\n但是……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "作为我的女儿，\\n作为一个心怀仁慈的人，\\n你还是能够为他人着想啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120166_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "嗯。魔兽收拾得\\n比我们想象得还要快嘛。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "教会骑士团……现在才到吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120166_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "接下来就由教会骑士团来接手。\\n继续任由你们处理的话，\\n我们的面子可就保不住了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "魔兽尚未被完全消灭，\\n许多居民也受了伤。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "眼下的情况，\\n多一双手就是多一份力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120166_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "你再继续插手的话就属于越权行为了。\\n我可以以妨碍公务为名请示开除你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贫民窟男子",
            "context": "快来人帮帮忙啊！\\n魔兽害我家起火了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贫民窟女子",
            "context": "我的弟弟受伤了！\\n谁能帮忙找人来为他治疗啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120166_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "现在没时间管你们！\\n我们正忙着讨伐魔兽呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（教会骑士团根本不在乎\\n“贫民窟”居民的窘境。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（他们在乎的只有\\n如何才能掩饰放任缺口扩大\\n而造成这种局面的失职。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（如果把这里交给他们，\\n就无法拯救住在这里的所有人。\\n我现在应该做的是——）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "爸……爸……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "！\\n席菈！你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我们一起……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "嗯……你说得对。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120166_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "唔！？迦道夫，你要干什么？\\n你要是敢擅自行动，别怪我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "想开除我就随你们的便吧。\\n既然眼前有人需要帮助，\\n我便会做我力所能及之事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_03_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
